data.description: Honey Stop the car! Better than brand new single owner home! 3bed 2bath with a large bonus room. Trailer/RV parking, fully fenced and manicured landscaping, upgrades galore and no rear neighbors. On demand hot water heater, owned water softener, man door off garage, tons of natural light, granite counters, upgraded trim and doors, stainless appliances, quiet back yard w large patio and so much more! Meticulously maintained and it shows. You couldn't duplicate this home w the builder for close to this price!
